Conclusion
You have successfully completed a comprehensive kill chain decomposition using Maltego CE. This lab demonstrated how to:

Visualize complex attack scenarios using graph-based analysis
Map attack stages to the Cyber Kill Chain framework
Identify critical entry points and attack infrastructure
Generate actionable intelligence for threat mitigation
This methodology is essential for threat intelligence analysts, incident responders, and security architects who need to understand and defend against advanced persistent threats. The visual analysis capabilities of Maltego CE provide crucial insights into attacker tactics, techniques, and procedures (TTPs) that traditional log analysis might miss.

The skills developed in this lab directly apply to real-world threat hunting, incident response, and proactive defense strategies in enterprise security operations.
